## ğŸ¯ Features

### Task Manager
- Add, view, edit, and delete tasks
- Mark tasks as completed
- Filter tasks by status (All, Completed, Pending)
- Optional: User authentication and task priorities

### Password Generator
- Generate secure passwords
- Select length and character options (uppercase, lowercase, digits, symbols)
- Copy-to-clipboard functionality
- Optional API endpoint for integration

